reviewText:
Pros:
-Black, white and red look nice together

Cons:
-Jankiest animations i've seen in a long time;
-Terrible pacing;
-The most bored Voice Actors of all time;
-Endless camera pans;
-Absolutely linear experience";
-No plot "hook" to get you interested in how it ends;
-Bizzare sound mixing

date:
 there might be about 3 different background tracks playing at the same time;
-Jarring leaps in asset quality;
-Detective board that literally spells out for you what to do and which you can't fail.

Straight line walking sim with no actual depth
